snippet.title: Earthworm Jim - PSP Gameplay [CANCELLED!]
snippet.description:
http://www.unseen64.net/

"Earthworm Jim PSP (working title) promised a re-imagined adventure for the PlayStation Portable, but eventually ended up being cancelled. It was to be an enhanced remake and would have incorporate new level designs, it promises to retain the feel and fun of the original Earthworm Jim game. It features an all new 3D graphic style, while still being reminiscent of the original." - wikipedia
